chapter-2
00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:15.000
核心功能概览

00:00:05.500 --> 00:00:09.200
📁 双面板文件浏览，支持列表与缩略图两种视图
📁 Dual-pane file browsing with list and thumbnail views

00:00:09.500 --> 00:00:14.800
🔍 内置预览面板，支持 <c.highlight>50+</c.highlight> 种文件格式
🔍 Built-in preview panel supporting <c.highlight>50+</c.highlight> file formats

chapter-3
00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:30.000
预览功能详解

00:00:15.500 --> 00:00:21.000
图片预览支持缩放、旋转、取色器
Image preview with zoom, rotate, and color picker

00:00:21.500 --> 00:00:27.300
Office 文档可在 <c.highlight>纯文本</c.highlight> 和 <c.highlight>格式化</c.highlight> 间切换
Office docs switchable between text and formatted views

00:00:27.800 --> 00:00:33.500
支持 PDF 搜索、代码语法高亮、Markdown 渲染
PDF search, code highlighting, Markdown rendering

chapter-4
00:00:34.000 --> 00:00:50.000
高级特性

00:00:34.200 --> 00:00:40.000
压缩包内文件列表预览（zip, tar, rar, 7z）
Archive content listing preview (zip, tar, rar, 7z)

00:00:40.500 --> 00:00:46.800
预览窗口可弹出为独立窗口
Detachable preview window for multi-monitor setups

00:00:47.000 --> 00:00:53.000
文件名快速搜索与正则表达式过滤
Quick file search with regex filtering

